<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-4bw+/aepP/YC94hEpVNVgiZdgIC5+VKNBQNGCHeKRQN+PtmoHDEXuppvnDJzQIu9" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title>New Activity</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Dopamine App</h1>

    <div class="container">
       <h2>Other Activity: <%= activity.activity %></h2>
       <h3>Date: <%= activity.date %></h3>
       <h3>Sun Exposure (Minutes): <%= activity.sun %></h3>
       <h3>Social Exposure (Minutes): <%= activity.social %></h3>
       <h3>Sleep Exposure (Minutes): <%= activity.sleep %></h3>
       <br/>
       <h3>What emotions does eating this activity make you feel when it started?</h3>
       <p>
        <%= activity.happy_begin %><br/>
        <%= activity.sad_begin %><br/>
        <%= activity.mad_begin %><br/>
        <%= activity.excited_begin %><br/>
        <%= activity.scared_begin %><br/>
        <%= activity.apathy_begin %><br/>
    </p>

    <h3>What emotions does eating this activity make you feel when you are done?</h3>
       <p>
        <%= activity.happy_done %><br/>
        <%= activity.sad_done %><br/>
        <%= activity.mad_done %><br/>
        <%= activity.excited_done %><br/>
        <%= activity.scared_done %><br/>
        <%= activity.apathy_done %><br/>
    </p>
<p><b>Notes: </b><%= activity.note %><br/></p>
    <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">Homepage</a>
    <!--<a href="/entries/edit/<%=activity.id %>" class="btn btn-info">Edit</a>-->
</div>
</body>
</html>